The ISOM 1:10000 symbol set can be created from the 1:15000 version by following these steps:
- Map -> Scale map ... from 15000 to 10000, all options ticked on
- set north line patterns spacing from 50mm to 40mm
- delete the oo mapper logo and copy over the original version without adjusting scale 
      
The ISSOM 1:4000 symbol set can be created from the 1:5000 version by following these steps:
- Map -> Scale map ... from 5000 to 4000, DEACTIVATE ALL OPTIONS
- set north line patterns spacing from 30mm to 37.5mm